《'''老妇杀手'''》（{{lang-en|The Ladykillers}}）是2004年上映的美国[[黑色幽默|黑色幽默]]电影，由[[科恩兄弟|科恩兄弟]]执导。<ref name="The Ladykillers 2004">{{cite web|url=http://alt.tcm.turner.com/tcmdb/title/452160/Ladykillers-The/full-credits.html|title=The Ladykillers 2004|work=[[特纳经典电影频道|特纳经典电影频道]]|location=[[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]|publisher=[[透納廣播公司|透納廣播公司]] ([[華納媒體|華納媒體]])|accessdate=2016-07-11|archive-date=2018-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713103554/http://alt.tcm.turner.com/tcmdb/title/452160/Ladykillers-The/full-credits.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>剧本是根据1955年由{{tsl|en|William Rose (screenwriter)|威廉·罗斯|}}编剧的英国伊灵喜剧同名电影改编的。<ref name="The Ladykillers 1955">{{cite web|url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/80720/The-Ladykillers/full-credits.html|title=The Ladykillers 1955|work=[[特纳经典电影频道|特纳经典电影频道]]|location=[[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]|publisher=[[透納廣播公司|透納廣播公司]] ([[華納媒體|華納媒體]])|accessdate=2016-07-11|archive-date=2019-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190103055840/http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/80720/The-Ladykillers/full-credits.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

科恩兄弟与汤姆·雅各布森、[[巴里·索南菲尔德|巴里·索南菲尔德]]和{{tsl|en|Barry Josephson|巴里·约瑟夫森|}}一起制作了这部电影。主演有[[汤姆·汉克斯|汤姆·汉克斯]]、{{tsl|en|Irma P. Hall|艾玛·霍尔|}}、[[馬龍·韋恩斯|馬龍·韋恩斯]]、[[J·K·西蒙斯|J·K·西蒙斯]]、[[马泰_(华裔演员)|马泰]]和{{tsl|en|Ryan Hurst|瑞恩·赫斯特|}}，这是科恩兄弟第一次与汤姆·汉克斯合作，也是科恩兄弟第一次翻拍电影。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Coenesque - The Ladykillers|url = http://www.coenbrothers.net/lady.html|website = www.coenbrothers.net|accessdate = 2015-12-02|archive-date = 2017-07-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170716184216/http://www.coenbrothers.net/lady.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>这是第一部乔尔和伊桑·科恩同时担任制片和导演的电影；之前，乔尔一直被认为是导演，伊森是制片人。

《老妇杀手》上映后收到的评价褒贬不一，一些影评人认为这部剧是科恩兄弟较弱的一部作品。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vulture.com/2016/02/every-coen-brothers-movie-ranked.html |title=Every Coen Brothers Movie, Ranked From Worst to Best |last=Ebiri |first=Bilge |publisher=New York Media |date=2016-02-05 |accessdate=2016-12-09 |archive-date=2020-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200601141313/https://www.vulture.com/2016/02/every-coen-brothers-movie-ranked.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://www.gq.com/story/the-definitive-ranking-of-all-17-coen-brothers-movies |title=The Definitive Ranking of All 17 Coen Brothers Movies |last=Gordon |first=Devin |magazine=GQ |date=2016-02-01 |accessdate=2016-12-09 |archive-date=2021-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215130945/https://www.gq.com/story/the-definitive-ranking-of-all-17-coen-brothers-movies |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2016/02/05/our-definitive-ranking-of-every-coen-brothers-film/ |title=Our definitive ranking of every Coen brothers film |last=Hornaday |first=Ann |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=2016-02-05 |accessdate=2016-12-09 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108101606/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2016/02/05/our-definitive-ranking-of-every-coen-brothers-film/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

